the physical underpinnings of many methods in the field used to\ncontrol and enhance free-electron radiation. Namely, the framework points to\nthe central role played by the photonic eigenmodes in controlling the output\nproperties of free-electron radiation (e.g., frequency, directionality, and\npolarization). [... see full abstract in paper]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Aug 2022 22:28:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2022 13:59:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-18"}
