odel. A sensitive test for the kick model will be the\nredshift evolution of the BNS merger rate since this is effectively a direct\nmeasure of the delay-time distribution for mergers. For our best fitting\nvalues, we find that the peak of the BNS merger rate is the present-day.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2022 02:26:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2022 01:27:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2023 23:23:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
