f PCNs. Finally, we postulate a new\ncomputational model for carbon nitride materials that encompasses the most\nimportant structural motifs and shows a bandgap of ca. 2.9 eV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2022 11:11:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-05"}
